<plot>A modern, multiracial, materialistic couple living in Hong Kong busy themselves with small talk, sex and money. They never discuss their shared dream visions of a higher spiritual reality, which they disregard as unreal. But, led by a benevolent dream guide, they go deeper into these visions, eventually leaving the material world behind.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?554320</url></doc>
